To install java, u need to install JDK.

JDK: Java development kit hota hai, jisme we have everything, like we can write code, we can compile it and finally we can run.

Companies like Oracle, Amazon etc have written their JDK, lagbhag sab same hi hota hai but ofcourse difference in license.

Pehle Oracle free me provide krta tha ab usne bhi paid kr diya.

1995 me sun microsystems company ne create kiya JAVA and in 2006 made it opensource as a project OENJDK Project.
